snippet.title: Radiator 1-3, Much Madness (HL2 mod trailer)
snippet.description:
Semi-episodic experimental single player mod for Half-Life 2: Episode Two. 

This mod is about: the short story, play and poem. California. Cynicism. Psychological repression. Gay marriage. Crappy dates. Homeostasis. regret. Growing up. Government bureaucracy. Death.

Coming March / April 2010. Visit the website: http://www.radiator.debacle.us

Music: a dashing piano cover of the Pixies' "Where is My Mind" by Maxence Cyrin (check out his other stuff on YouTube, it's amazing.)
